GLENN-COLUSA IRRIGATION DISTRICT, Appellant, v. R. J. McMULLEN et al., Appellees. No. 8403. ■Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 15, 1937. A. L. Cowell, of Stockton, Cal., and ■ Hankins & Hankins, of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. W. Coburn Cook, of Turlock, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and MATHEWS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of appellees, ordered this cause advanced for hearing, submitted, and order of District Court affirmed.
